\@@_msg_new:nn { Multiple~tags }
  {
    Multiple~tags.\\
    You~can't~use~twice~the~command~\token_to_str:N\tag\ 
    in~a~line~of~the~environment~\{\l_@@_type_env_str\}. \\
    If~you~go~on,~the~tag~'#1'~will~be~used.
  }
